s inventory storage methods and improved sales efficiency and drastically reduced the level of discrepancies to 0 discrepancies by year end;\n4.' || chr(9) || 'Restructured monthly team KPI and introduced client building metrics and increased return sales by 35%;\n5.' || chr(9) || 'Worked closely with watch merchandiser to achieve store’s highest number of pieces ever sold in throughout the 6 months of 2009.', 
