upport new store opening.\n10. Recruit, train and manage e-commerce team in China (5 departments and 15 staff). Build/Optimize internal processes to improve the effectiveness of daily operation.', '电商运营@@@40___电商营销@@@30___Merchandising@@@30', null, 0, 221003, '170421220320395010124987308217', 'Clare SHAO', to_date('24-04-2017 10:35:09', 'dd-mm-yyyy hh24:mi:ss'), 30, '公司发展放缓', '0', 0, null, '2014年销售业绩从400万增长到1200万。\n升级电商平台，重组团队。', null);
