        '1. Executive manager-Regional Operations Center (Eastern China):' || chr(9) || '\n* Carry out the company operation policy, in charge of the HR skills and Admin affairs;\n* Take charge of the sales department daily routine, to deal with the emergency ASAP;\n* Communicate with different department to complete the affairs;\n* Monitor the achievement of the budgets by analyzing daily sales figures in order to suggest \n* Follow up the project investment interests and help finish the new shop opening process;\n* Some of shops get 10% increase in 2011, and 20% increase in 2012\n* Control the new shop costs, looking for the sale promotions. \n\n2. Jobs in Watch Management Dept:\n* Lead integration of business procedures with all departments, use the group resources to strengthen a rational work arrangement and ensure achieving the sales target. \n* Help all department to establish and effective team work mechanism, solve communication difficulties in all departments to ensure a smooth business flow. \n* Lead analysis on sales date submitted by all sale offices in East China, and analyses sales data of all brands. \n* Lead distribution of sales targets to all areas and monitor their sales works. \n* Coordinate among all departments and deal with accidents timely.\n* According to market analysis to determine the operating brand Maintain close communication with the shopping mall management, strive for the best mode of cooperation. \n* With the brand to maintain good relations of cooperation.\n\n3. Administration & HR Manager:\n* Lead company cultural value development; provide HR resources for company long-term development.\n* Lead establishment and management of administration files, apply for business license and carry out management.\n* Control and mange company administration expense.\n* Establish company assets management information, organize materials procurement and control procurement expenses. \n* Establish good work environment in company, fire fighting 