values (10628, 10136, -1, -1, null, to_date('23-04-2017 13:18:01', 'dd-mm-yyyy hh24:mi:ss'), to_date('23-04-2017 19:27:03', 'dd-mm-yyyy hh24:mi:ss'), '170423131801536010148688792749', 130001, '2015/04', '至今', 'BV[柏蒂.温妮达（中国）贸易有限公司]', null, '奢侈品', null, 'Area Manager - East China', null, 47000, 60, '基本工资*13+年度奖金（约1个月薪水）', 'GM', '10', 
        '1.' || chr(9) || 'Take in charge of 10 stores in Guizhou/Fujian /Zhejiang/ Jiangsu/Hubei/ Hunan province, there’re Guiyang/ Xiamen/Wenzhou/ Ningbo/Hangzhou/ Suzhou/ Wuxi/ Nanjing/Wuhan/Changsha pop-up store. And among these stores Hangzhou/Nanjing/Wuhan/Xiamen stores are belonged to key stores level which with bigger potential market and higher sales performance and contribution;\n2.' || chr(9) || 'Maximizes the potential of the Area, exploiting business opportunities, corporate with LLD to seek more chances to develop branding share in the local market，to know more clearly and detail for the competitors;\n3.' || chr(9) || 'Holds the Boutique Managers accountable to set SMART goals for team members and reach a higher level of performance. Identifies issues/challenges, prioritizes them and defines clear action plans to ensure the best results in the Area. Supports and develops the Store Managers to do the same;\n4.' || chr(9) || 'Proposes and accepts new ideas and change initiatives, shows an interest in new experiences, best practices, projects. Challenges the Boutique Managers to generate creative and valuable ideas to improve their business;\n5.' || chr(9) || 'Analyses store, merchandise and market data, knows how to reference and utilize data to put actions in place to increase results. Supports and develops the Boutique Managers to do the same. Communicates clearly numerical data (KPIs, YTD sales vs budget, YTD sales vs LY;\n6.' || chr(9) || 'Ensures Boutique Managers build effective teams, celebrating success, sharing information, seeking for contribution, integrating newcomers and leading as example to manage different personalities and/or nationalities. Ensures that the induction procedure is adhered to and follow up training provided;\n7.' || chr(9) || 'Inspires trust by displaying honesty. Communicates company strategy and the long term vision for the store to all retail staff, in a consistent, clear, concise and inspirational manner;\n8.' || chr(9) || 'Keeps motivation alive and emotions under control during difficult situations, creates a sense of belonging and a positive environment in which people strive for excellence.', '店铺销售运营管理@@@50___新店开设@@@20___人员管理团队建设@@@30', '低调、质量及工艺 C Bottega Veneta自1966年始，汇集意大利出色传统皮革工匠，以上等的材质、卓越的手工艺、现代的功能，以及创新的设计为宗旨，秉承瑰丽细致、注重美感和秉具个人风格的一贯特质。匠心呈现男士系列、女士系列、家居艺术及香氛系列等。', 0, 221003, '170419134445177010134920098730', 
        'Jane LI', to_date('23-04-2017 19:27:03', 'dd-mm-yyyy hh24:mi:ss'), 30, '希望加入更高端的品牌。', '0', 0, null, '1. 2016年业绩对比去年有17%的增长；\n2. 开设厦门店和长沙店；\n3. 人员稳定，10个店长流失1名，提升了2个ASM；\n4. 东区从接手时的6家店发展到现在的10家电，业绩稳定增长。', null);
