mbers;\n4. Reviewed team members’ performance, and carried out action plans for improvement;\n5. Manager on duty / floor control\n6. Ensured store’s smooth and normal operation;\n7. Arranged manpower on floor and motivated staff to achieve daily target;\n8. Handled client complaints and other non-selling tasks.', 'drive daisy full cycle to support retail@@@60___planning and buying@@@30___team management and training@@@10', null, 0, 221003, 
