values (10586, 10125, -1, -1, null, to_date('23-04-2017 11:05:26', 'dd-mm-yyyy hh24:mi:ss'), to_date('24-04-2017 02:32:47', 'dd-mm-yyyy hh24:mi:ss'), '170423103349630010101152096563', 130001, '2012/11', '2013/05', 'Balmain[褒曼商贸（上海）有限公司]', null, null, null, 'Merchandising Manager', null, null, null, null, null, null, '1. Pre-Season Merchandise Planning\na) Conduct analysis based on historical sell-in and sell-through data to identify top selling articles and slow moving articles, and identify the key drivers for success or failure.\nb) Execute OTB planning and by category sales forecast and workout division level buy plan. 4 times oversees buying trip in Paris and 4 times buying domestically.\nc) Control margin, SKU count and conduct detail assortment plan based on historical performance.\nd) Work with product marketing team to provide feedback on trade needs and new seasonal range.\ne) Place order with good assortment and initial launch package, provide order compliance check and provide detail analysis.\n\n2. In-Season Planning & Allocation\na) Lead in the process to provide ongoing product and category performance and quantitative analysis of sell though, inventory level, markdown plan etc.\nb) Provide seasonal deep dive analysis by store and performance tracking reports to develop mark down strategy and support markdown and clearance process.\nc) Maintain & Monitor compliance of pre-season buy and P&L as well as planning calendar.\n\n3. Allocation and Replenishment\na) Provide new store allocation, regular replenishment, stock transfer and inventory management.\nb) Review inventory turnover and conduct outlet rollout plan, design seasonal promotion and product pricing for all stores and outlet.\nc) Design concept & story and provide material training.', '@@@', null, 0, null, '170421220320395010124987308217', 'Clare SHAO', to_date('24-04-2017 02:32:47', 'dd-mm-yyyy hh24:mi:ss'), 0, null, '0', 0, null, null, null);
