values (10587, 10125, -1, -1, null, to_date('23-04-2017 11:05:26', 'dd-mm-yyyy hh24:mi:ss'), to_date('24-04-2017 02:32:47', 'dd-mm-yyyy hh24:mi:ss'), '170423103349630010101152096563', 130001, '2012/06', '2012/11', 'GAP[盖璞(上海)商业有限公司]', null, null, null, 'Associate Manager, Distribution', null, null, null, null, null, null, '1. Distribution and Replenishment\na) Support in driving the financial success of multiple divisions by meeting or exceeding sales, gross margin, gross margin return on investment (GMROI) and inventory turn goals.\nb) Communicate division-level merchandising plans within division and translate to distribution strategies that support planned merchandising and financial objectives.\nc) Supervise and approve initial inventory releases, ensure consistent and profitable in-season replenishment and replenishment strategies. \nd) Inform team of divisional strategies for packing, pre-packs, size balancing and inventory balancing within multiple pools of inventory upon guidance from the manager.\n\n2. Analysis and Strategy\na) Develop Divisional distribution strategies to capture location-based opportunity. Guide and approve inventory parameter and replenishment plans for basic styles. \nb) Sponsor analysis and cross-functional partnerships that will identify and quantify size selling, geographic and store-attribute opportunities; ensure follow through on execution of strategies.', '@@@', null, 0, null, '170421220320395010124987308217', 'Clare SHAO', to_date('24-04-2017 02:32:47', 'dd-mm-yyyy hh24:mi:ss'), 0, null, '0', 0, null, null, null);
