and safety policies, control office daily affairs.\n* Lead an overall planning of company administration affairs by company facts, give guidance and coordination, and help on cooperation with government.', null, null, 0, null, '20161101000000999000000001', '白子牙', to_date('23-04-2017 13:35:24', 'dd-mm-yyyy hh24:mi:ss'), 0, null, '0', 0, null, null, null);
