nline system management and warehouse staff sales operations procedures;\n6.' || chr(9) || 'Budgeted, managed, and successfully executed China zone’s first long distance ready to wear sale;\n7.' || chr(9) || 'Coordinated entire store opening logistics for 2 Shanghai global stores, Chongqing global store Shenyang store.\n\nJun 2009 - Mar 2010' || chr(9) || 'Plaza 66 Shanghai Global Store - Leather Goods Category Supervisor' || chr(9) || '\n\nResponsibilities:\n1.' || chr(9) || 'Managed the number 1 in leathergoods sales category, a multi-million dollar per annum business, including personally managing made to order and fashion show products for top VICs;\n2.' || chr(9) || 'Led a team of 16 senior sales and sales associates;\n3.' || chr(9) || 'Increased leather good year on year sales by 3% and increased penetration rate by 6% to account for 75% of overall store sales;\n4.' || chr(9) || 'Devised and executed Shanghai store, China’s first, concierge greeter service that rolled out nation wide;\n5.' || chr(9) || 'Revamped leather goods best seller inventory storage and managed monthly rotation that led to a 16% increased LFL sales;\n6.' || chr(9) || 'Restructured centrally managed small leather goods storage and display and improved sales by 12% year-to-date;\n7.' || chr(9) || 'Selected for Ulaanbaatar store attachment and identified areas for operational improvements, consulted with UB store manager and facilitated to improve store daily operations at management level and on the selling floor.\n\nJul 2008 - Jun 2009' || chr(9) || 'Hangzhou Tower Store - Watch & Jewelry and Shoes Category Supervisor\n\nResponsibilities:\n1.' || chr(9) || 'Managed 2 categories and security detail comprising of 8 senior sales and sales associates along with 12 security guards;\n2.' || chr(9) || 'Introduced key metric systems and increased overall sales in shoes category by 19% versus previous year, ranking number 1 in growth and number 2 in sales volume;\n3.' || chr(9) || 'Introduced shoe