        'Jan 2016 - Feb 2017' || chr(9) || 'Area Manager - Retail Luxury for China\n\nResponsibilities:\n1.' || chr(9) || 'Managing China zone 10 luxury stores located Shanghai, Beijing, Changchun, Shenyang, Hangzhou, Suzhou, Nanning, Ningbo and reporting directly to VP Retail Luxury of Greater China & Southeast Asia;\n2.' || chr(9) || 'Partnering with APAC and China merchandisers, on runway buys, store reallocations and increased women''s apparel sales growth of 220% with increased sell-through by 31%, and men''s apparel sales growth of 5%;\n3.' || chr(9) || 'Launched key metrics training program and increased overall UPT by 5% and VPT by 36%, and conversion increased by 15%;\n4.' || chr(9) || 'Managed and partnered with cross functional teams and landlords for 2 successful store openings in Beijing (luxury) and Dalian (kids).\n\nMar 2015 - Jan 2016' || chr(9) || 'Area Manager - North China, Chengdu, Chongqing\n\nResponsibilities:\n1.' || chr(9) || 'Managed 11 stores, including 2 Ralph Lauren luxury stores (Shenyang, Changchun), 8 kids stores (Beijing, Changchun, Dalian, Shenyang, Chengdu, Chongqing), and 1 golf store (Beijing). Led a team of 7 managers as direct reports;\n2.' || chr(9) || 'Grew comp store business to double to triple digit in selected stores: 31% growth in golf store, 200% in Chengdu, 9% in Beijing SKP, 2% in Beijing Scitech;\n3.' || chr(9) || 'Concurrently led zone wide POS system upgrade project and worked cross function with APAC and China functional teams;\n4.' || chr(9) || 'Concurrently led China zone CRM. Developed and implemented successful CRM campaigns focusing on customer acquisition to VIC growth and retention for all channels (luxury, kids, outlet), including China zone''s first loyal and "At-Risk" customer programs, and VICs for outlet channel. Resulted in successful overall VICs customers: luxury +45%, kids +102%, increased overall VIC sales by +28% and existing VIC sales contribution from 21% to 28%;\n5.' || chr(9) || 'Spearheaded successful customer data capture campaigns for China zone and achieved highest growth rate in APAC for both customer associated transactions +32%, and valid customer rate +23%. Ranked overall number 3 in APAC, up from number 6;\n6.' || chr(9) || 'Involved in service/ mystery shopper committee. Implemented key programs for successful growth in mystery shopper scores. Increase in 21 basis points for luxury and kids stores on average, with 2 stores ranked highest in APAC;\n7.' || chr(9) || 'Launched monthly multiple zone wide incentive plans for both luxury and kids channel that saw monthly increase and sell through in category and overall sales in both kids and luxury channels\n8.' || chr(9) || 'Managed and partnered with cross functional team and landlords on 2 successful store openings: Changchun (luxury and kids).\n\nSept 2012 - Mar 2015' || chr(9) || 'Store Manager - Shanghai Peninsula & Park Place  \n\nResponsibilities:\n1.' || chr(9) || 'Shanghai Peninsula: \na.' || chr(9) || 'Led the Peninsula store and attained the number 1store in sales revenue in China for 3 consecutive years, with year on year growth:  17% growth v. FY14, 16% growth v. FY13, 28% growth v. FY12 and ranked number 1 store (revenue) in China consecutively for 3 years;\nb.' || chr(9) || 'Devised and implemented CRM plan, resulting with an increase in return sales by 215% in the 1st year and 200% in the 2nd year;\nc.' || chr(9) || 'Implemented KPI for daily ops and staff management, resulting to 45% increase in overall sales per staff;\n2.' || chr(9) || 'Shanghai Park Place:' || chr(9) || '\na.' || chr(9) || 'Led a 45% increase in sales in 2 quarters versus year before and achieved the number 2 store in sales revenue in China for FY14 end;\nb.' || chr(9) || 'Revised VIC store program and increased VIC sales by 25% and developed 18% more VICs LFL.', 
        'Strategy & Planning@@@30___Store Operation@@@50___People Development@@@20', null, 0, 221004, '170419134656067010114745958955', 'Steven ZHOU', to_date('24-04-2017 10:53:56', 'dd-mm-yyyy hh24:mi:ss'), 0, '公司开始关店铺，留下2家Luxury，希望更多的Challenge。', '0', 0, null, '1. 从管多店的Store Manager在2015年被晋升为Area Manager，负责北区，直到负责全国的Luxury Store。\n2. 负责全国CRM，包括kids，outlet和luxury，创造了Royal Profile，Double了Kids的业绩，Luxury增长了50%，VIP增长了30%。\n3. 负责的11家Stores业绩增长了12%；\n4. Golf Store增加了31%；\n4. 开店时间减少20%；\n5. 负责全国的Luxury Store期间Gross Margin增长了近10%；\n6. 女装业务增长了220%；', null);
